<plot>The e-cop Tom Beckwith has just quit his police job in order to study psychology. But his professor Lauren Porter is more interested in his criminalogical abilities than in his progress in psychology. Because of traumatic circumstances during her childhood she is suffering under schizofrenia, and everything looks like her other ego has just killed somebody. So Tom Beckwith tries to help her by taking over the job to observate her combining his professional abilities as an ex-cop and his just gained knowledge about psychology.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?486368</url></doc>
